227
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Super.

228
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Doktor namasti.

229
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Baš ljetko to zvuči.

230
00:11:12,000 --> 00:11:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Svi se obraća s poštovanjem.

231
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] I živiš u točno određene četvrti

232
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] u kojeg baš žive svi koji su slični tebi.

233
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] I došao ti sad.

234
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:20,000
